        "product_description": {
            "value": "Meet HEROCLIP Large in Tidal - the world's first 3-in-1 clip and hook that can hang just about anything, just about anywhere! Engineered for versatility and durability, the Heroclip Large combines a carabiner clip, swivel hook, and rubber grip tip into one compact, easy-to-use tool. HANG STUFF SECURELY: The Heroclip Large holds up to 100 lbs, and its rubber tip creates optimal grip so your gear stays put. It's 40% larger than the Medium, making it perfect for bulky and heavy items. COMPACT DESIGN: The hook and clip nest neatly together when not in use, so the Heroclip stays out of the way until you need it. Size Large measures 4.1\" wide and 5.24\" high when closed, expanding to 7.25\" high when open. COUNTLESS USES: Ideal for bulky outdoor gear, garage organization, shopping carts, strollers, backpacks, luggage, camping equipment, and so much more. The 360-degree swivel hook lets you position your gear at any angle. Made from strong, lightweight aluminum and built to last, the Heroclip Large is a must-have for adventurers, organizers, and anyone who needs to hang, hold, or carry their essentials on the go. Backed by a Manufacturer Limited Lifetime Warranty for lasting peace of mind.",
            "is_required": true,
            "source": "ai",
